title: SpeedBit Software SpeedOptimizer 3
description:
SpeedBit Software SpeedOptimizer 3 (build 3.0.9.6) | 4.06 MB

Speed Up Your PC & Network for Best performance. SpeedOptimizer will speed up your PC and network with a click. SpeedOptimizer analyzes your computer's hardware and operating system and performs a series of optimizations that allow smooth and trouble-free operation. SpeedOptimizer 3.0 includes network optimization, registry cleaner, file sweeper, startup manager and much more!
